## Deployed Services

VPN007 deploys **5 long-running services** plus a certbot utility container:

| # | Service | Container | Port / Access | Description |
|---|---------|-----------|---------------|-------------|
| 1 | **Reverse Proxy** | `reverse_proxy` (nginx) | 443/tcp{% if enable_port_8443 %}, 8443/tcp{% endif %}, 80/tcp (ACME only) | L4 SNI routing + L7 path routing with TLS termination |
| 2 | **Xray (VLESS+Reality)** | `three_x_ui` (3x-ui + embedded Xray) | Internal port {{ xray_internal_port }}, accessed via SNI `{{ reality_sni }}` on 443/tcp | Anti-DPI VPN tunnel mimicking legitimate TLS 1.3 |
| 3 | **3x-ui Web Panel** | `three_x_ui` | `https://{{ domain }}{{ xui_path_prefix }}/` (IP-restricted) | Browser-based Xray management panel |
| 4 | **AmneziaWG VPN** | `amneziawg` (host network) | {{ awg_listen_port or "random high port" }}/udp | WireGuard-based VPN with DPI-resistant obfuscation |
| 5 | **AmneziaWG Panel** | `amneziawg` | `https://{{ domain }}{{ awg_panel_path_prefix }}/` (IP-restricted) | Web interface for AmneziaWG peer management |
| 6 | **Tailscale** | `tailscale` (host network) | Overlay network (no exposed ports) | Mesh VPN for secure management and inter-node connectivity |
| 7 | **Cover Site** | `cover_site` (nginx) | Served as default on `https://{{ domain }}/` | Legitimate website for plausible deniability |

**Utility containers:**

- **certbot** — Invoked via `docker compose run --rm certbot` for TLS certificate
  acquisition and renewal. Not a long-running service.

