### Recommended Requirements

| Resource | Recommended | Notes |
|----------|-------------|-------|
| **CPU** | 2+ vCPU | Multiple concurrent VPN clients, AmneziaWG kernel module compilation |
| **RAM** | 4 GB | Headroom for Docker image updates and log retention |
| **Disk** | 30 GB | Docker image layers, log retention, certificate storage |

> **Note:** Disk usage increases with the number of VPN clients, Docker image
> layers, and log retention. Additional resources may be needed when traffic
> forwarding to a secondary VM is enabled.

